org.apache.zab

Class SimpleLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zab.SimpleLog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Log

    public class SimpleLog
extends Object
implements Log
    This class implements the Log interface. The format of a Transaction log is as follows: 

     log-file     := [ transactions ]

 transactions := transaction | transaction transactions

 transaction  := zxid body-length body

 zxid         := epoch(int) xid(int)

 body-length  := length of body(int)

 body         := byte array
